#bug report 

##bug1: script not working
**why it happened:*8 script tag was in <head> before HTML loaded
**how i fixedit:** moved <script src="index.js"></script> to just before </body>

##bug 2: register button not cllickable 
**reason:** css layer/pointer-events issue
**how i fixed it** added pointer-events:auto; and z-index;10; in.submit-btn

##bug 3: counter increases incorrectly 
**reason:**spotLeft treated as string and addition used
**how i fixed it ** changed spotsLeft to number and used subtraction 

##bug4: submit button does nothing 
**reason:** no submit event listener and incorrect form ID
** how i fixed it** added form.addEventListener('submit',...) amd corrected form ID
